%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d8a2b2adee5c2406fb0c50c44244ff03, type: 3}
  m_Name: DlgTree_DebtCollector
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueId: dlg_debt_collector
  npcCharacter: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
  playerCharacter: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9b89d477ed6fc0d4f93157527a06fd71, type: 2}
  greetingLines:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
    text: What? The hell do you want? So how exactly is that chick planning to settle
      her debt?!
    typingSpeed: 30
    waitForInput: 1
  choices:
  - choiceLabel: Relationship with the victim
    npcMoodAnimator: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 8019ac8194e864224a545395232ce48d, type: 2}
    npcMoodSprite: {fileID: 0}
    responseLines:
    - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
      text: She borrowed money to gamble and dug herself into a massive debt. So
        now I'm the one who's gotta go out and collect?
      typingSpeed: 30
      waitForInput: 1
    - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
      text: Been threatening her, scaring the hell outta her, and she still wouldn't
        cough up the cash. Kept making promises left and right, and even a few days
        ago she still didn't pay a damn thing.
      typingSpeed: 30
      waitForInput: 1
    - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
      text: That's a huge amount of money. If she's dead, who the hell's gonna pay
        me back?!
      typingSpeed: 30
      waitForInput: 1
    testimonyCue: {fileID: 0}
    hideAfterChosen: 1
  - choiceLabel: Information about the victim's personality
    npcMoodAnimator: {fileID: 9100000, guid: c2b33e3c970c744d6ac84d20f90d8ca2, type: 2}
    npcMoodSprite: {fileID: 0}
    responseLines:
    - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
      text: "Huh!? She was obsessed with getting rich \u2014 had connections everywhere,
        knew how to do business \u2014 but she was hooked on gambling bad. Burned
        every damn cent at the tables."
      typingSpeed: 30
      waitForInput: 1
    - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e5df2bb2a293491fad90bfc820ff942, type: 2}
      text: Kept saying her so-called 'fortune numbers' were gonna hit big and she'd
        pay everything back. Tch, Lucky numbers my a-.
      typingSpeed: 30
      waitForInput: 1
    testimonyCue: {fileID: 0}
    hideAfterChosen: 1
  farewellLines: []
